'''2007年友誼快線爆炸案'''發生於2007年2月19日子夜前後的[[恐怖襲擊|恐怖襲擊]]，案中來往[[印度|印度]][[德里|德里]]和[[巴基斯坦|巴基斯坦]][[拉合爾|拉合爾]]的[[薩姆豪塔快線|薩姆豪塔快線]]（又稱'''友誼快線'''）<ref name="BBC">{{cite news|title=Dozens dead in India train blast|publisher=[[BBC_News|BBC News]]|date=2007-02-19|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/south_asia/6374377.stm|accessdate=2007-02-21|archive-date=2019-06-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190604120303/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/south_asia/6374377.stm|dead-url=no}} Retrieved on Feb. 19, 2007</ref>
<ref name="Time">{{cite news|title=66 Die in India-Pakistan Train Attack|author=Muneeza Naqvi|publisher=[[美聯社|美聯社]]|date=2007-02-19|url=http://www.time.com/time/world/article/0,8599,1591471,00.html|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://archive.is/20120525161604/www.time.com/time/world/article/0,8599,1591471,00.html|archivedate=2012-05-25|accessdate=2007-02-21}} Retrieved on Feb. 19, 2007</ref>發生爆炸，69人死亡，數十人受傷。 <ref>{{cite news|title=Toll reaches to 68 in Samjhauta Express explosions|author=|publisher=Islamic Republic News Agency|date=2007-02-20|url=http://www2.irna.ir/en/news/view/menu-239/0702206010190550.htm|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070224134119/http://www2.irna.ir/en/news/view/menu-239/0702206010190550.htm|archivedate=2007-02-24|accessdate=2007-02-21}} Retrieved on Feb. 20, 2007</ref>死者中大部分為巴基斯坦平民，其餘為印度平民和守衛列車的印裔軍裝人員。<ref name="Reuters">{{cite news|title=At least 66 killed in India-Pakistan train blast|author=Y.P. Rajesh|publisher=[[Reuters|Reuters]]|date=2007-02-19|url=http://in.today.reuters.com/news/newsArticle.aspx?type=topNews&storyID=2007-02-19T173713Z_01_NOOTR_RTRJONC_0_India-288273-18.xml&archived=False|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070301153727/http://in.today.reuters.com/news/newsArticle.aspx?type=topNews&storyID=2007-02-19T173713Z_01_NOOTR_RTRJONC_0_India-288273-18.xml&archived=False|archivedate=2007-03-01|accessdate=2007-02-21}} Retrieved on Feb. 19, 2007</ref>當列車剛駛過[[印度|印度]]城市[[帕尼帕特|巴尼伯特]]（{{lang|en|Panipat}}）的Diwana車站時，第10和第11號車廂發生爆炸，距離[[新德里|新德里]]北面僅90公里。<ref name="Hindustan">{{cite news|title=66 killed as Samjhauta Express becomes terror target|author=Hitender Rao|publisher=Hindustan Times|date=2007-02-19|url=http://www.hindustantimes.com/news/181_1931712,0008.htm|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070221045956/http://www.hindustantimes.com/news/181_1931712%2C0008.htm|archivedate=2007-02-21|accessdate=2007-02-21}} Retrieved on Feb. 19, 2007</ref>事後在爆炸車廂內發現裝有爆炸裝置、易燃物品的手提包，有3個炸彈仍未引爆。其中一個手提包裝有1枚未引爆的炸彈、裝在透明膠盒內的電子計時器及盛有燃油和化學物的膠樽。<ref name="Reuters"/> 
其餘8個未受影響車卡其後照原訂路線駛往拉合爾。

印巴政府均譴責事件，並推測事件有意阻礙雙方改善關係，因為事件正正發生在巴國[[外長|外長]]{{link-en|胡爾希德·卡蘇里|Khurshid Mahmud Kasuri}}（{{lang|en|Khurshid Mahmud Kasuri}}）訪問新德里尋求重開兩國和平談判的前一天。 <ref name="Time"/>

== 各國反應 ==

=== 印度 ===
[[印度|印度]]鐵道部長{{link-en|拉鲁·普拉萨德·亚达夫|Lalu Prasad Yadav}}譴責事件<ref name="NDTV">{{cite news|title=Cross border tragedy: Samjhauta Express blasts kill 66|author=Alok Pandey, Rati R, Sushmit Sengupta, Vikram Chowdhury|publisher=[[NDTV|NDTV]]|date=2007-02-19|url=http://www.ndtv.com/template/template.asp?template=Attariblasts&id=21450&callid=0&category=National|accessdate=2007-02-21|archive-date=2007-02-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070221165400/http://www.ndtv.com/template/template.asp?template=Attariblasts&id=21450&callid=0&category=National|dead-url=no}} Retrieved on Feb. 19, 2007</ref>。他宣布賠償方案，死者家屬獲賠[[印度盧布|Rs.]] 1,000,000（約[[美元|US$]]22,750），傷者獲賠Rs. 50,000。<ref name="TH">{{cite news|title= Samjhauta Express firebombed, 67 killed|author= Praveen Swami|publisher= The Hindu|date= 2007-02-19|url= http://www.hindu.com/2007/02/20/stories/2007022012520100.htm|accessdate= 2007-02-21|archive-date= 2007-02-21|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20070221023502/http://www.hindu.com/2007/02/20/stories/2007022012520100.htm|dead-url= no}}</ref>印度內政部長[[希夫拉傑·維什瓦納特拉奧·帕蒂爾|希夫拉傑·維什瓦納特拉奧·帕蒂爾]]稱「幕後黑手與和平作對，並企圖破壞印度與鄰國改善中的關係」。[[印度總理|印度總理]][[曼莫汉·辛格|曼莫汉·辛格]]表示「痛苦和悲傷」，又聲言會抽出幕後主腦。<ref name="BBC"/>印度外長承諾向受影響巴國旅客的家屬發出簽證。<ref name="NDTV2">{{cite news |title=India offers visas after train attack |publisher=NDTV News |date=2007-02-19 |url=http://www.ndtv.com/template/template.asp?template=Attariblasts&slug=India+offers+visas+after+train+attack&id=101094&callid=1&category=National |accessdate=2007-02-21 |archive-date=2019-08-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190821221300/https://www.ndtv.com/news |dead-url=no }} Retrieved on Feb. 19, 2007</ref>印度分析家認為，事件不會影響印巴和平進程。<ref name="The Hindu">{{cite news |title=Keep the peace process on track |author=Siddharth Varadarajan |publisher=The Hindu |date=2007-02-20 |url=http://www.hindu.com/2007/02/20/stories/2007022005101000.htm |accessdate=2007-02-21 |archive-date=2007-02-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070221052900/http://www.hindu.com/2007/02/20/stories/2007022005101000.htm |dead-url=no }} Retrieved on Feb. 19, 2007</ref>

=== 巴基斯坦 ===
巴基斯坦政府的反應與印度類似，外長{{link-en|胡尔希德·卡苏里|Khurshid Mahmud Kasuri}}指事件是[[恐怖活动|恐怖活动]]，但不會阻礙他出訪印度的行程，又指應加快印巴和平進程。<ref name="Musharraf">{{cite news|title=Musharraf says train blasts won't sabotage peace|publisher=[[Reuters|Reuters]] News|date=2007-02-19|url=http://in.today.reuters.com/news/newsArticle.aspx?type=topNews&storyID=2007-02-19T142851Z_01_NOOTR_RTRJONC_0_India-288322-1.xml&archived=False|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070221124835/http://in.today.reuters.com/news/newsArticle.aspx?type=topNews&storyID=2007-02-19T142851Z_01_NOOTR_RTRJONC_0_India-288322-1.xml&archived=False|archivedate=2007-02-21|accessdate=2007-02-21}} Retrieved on Feb. 19, 2007</ref>[[巴基斯坦總統|巴基斯坦總統]][[佩尔韦兹·穆沙拉夫|佩尔韦兹·穆沙拉夫]]說：「類似的恐怖活動只會使雙方更堅定地達致彼此持續和平。」<ref name="Musharraf"/>他又相信印度會徹底調查事件。 <ref name="BBC"/>

=== 英國 ===
[[英國|英國]][[外交及聯邦事務部|外交及聯邦事務部]][[國務大臣|國務大臣]]{{link-en|金·豪尔斯|Kim Howells}}是「極度羞恥」的行為，又指英國會提供一切印巴兩國要求的協助，以將襲擊的幕後主腦繩之於法。<ref name="APP">{{cite news |title=British Government condemns bomb attack on India-Pakistan train |publisher=Associated Press of Pakistan |date=2007-02-19 |url=http://www.app.com.pk/en/index.php?option=com_content&task=view&id=4236&Itemid=2 |accessdate=2007-02-21 |archive-date=2007-09-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070927192844/http://www.app.com.pk/en/index.php?option=com_content&task=view&id=4236&Itemid=2 }} Retrieved on Feb. 19, 2007</ref>[[英籍亞裔|英籍巴裔]]社群團體稱襲擊是「卑鄙的行為」，要求儘快調查事件。<ref name="APP"/>

=== 美國 ===
[[白宮|白宮]]譴責事件，白宮[[發言人|發言人]]代表[[美國|美國]]政府向慘劇受害者致以慰問，又讚揚印巴兩國領袖，同時譴責意圖破壞兩國改善關係的人。<ref name="Reuters2">{{cite news|title=White House condemns those behind India train bombing|publisher=[[Reuters|Reuters]]|date=2007-02-19|url=http://in.today.reuters.com/news/newsArticle.aspx?type=topNews&storyID=2007-02-19T215920Z_01_NOOTR_RTRJONC_0_India-288360-1.xml&archived=False}}{{dead link|date=2017年11月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot }} Retrieved on Feb. 19, 2007</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=US condemns attack on Samjhauta Express|publisher=Press Trust of India|date=2007-02-20|url=http://www.hindu.com/thehindu/holnus/001200702201823.htm|accessdate=2007-02-21|archive-date=2008-05-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080523134747/http://www.hindu.com/thehindu/holnus/001200702201823.htm|dead-url=no}} Retrieved on Feb. 20, 2007</ref>

== 調查 ==
印度警方指出，手提包炸彈襲擊作案者起碼4至5人，有可能與武裝分子有關聯。<ref name="Reu">{{cite news|title=Police release sketches of bomb suspects|publisher=[[Reuters|Reuters]]|date=2007-02-20|url=http://in.today.reuters.com/news/newsArticle.aspx?type=topNews&storyID=2007-02-20T231318Z_01_NOOTR_RTRJONC_0_India-288416-7.xml&archived=False|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070222173946/http://in.today.reuters.com/news/newsArticle.aspx?type=topNews&storyID=2007-02-20T231318Z_01_NOOTR_RTRJONC_0_India-288416-7.xml&archived=False|archivedate=2007-02-22|accessdate=2007-02-21}} Retrieved on Feb. 20, 2007</ref>警方又發出兩名疑犯的拼圖，該兩人在爆炸發生前15分鐘離開列車。<ref name="Reu"/>其中一人年齡約35至36歲，體型較胖，深色皮膚，有[[鬍子|鬍子]]，另一人年齡約26至27歲，頭戴圍巾，兩人均操[[印度語|印度語]]。<ref name="Sky">{{cite news|title=Images Of Bomb Suspects|publisher=Sky News|date=2007-02-20|url=http://news.sky.com/skynews/article/0,,30000-1252387,00.html|accessdate=2007-02-21|archive-date=2008-12-04|archive-url=https://archive.is/20081204065332/http://news.sky.com/skynews/article/0,,30000-1252387,00.html|dead-url=no}} Retrieved on Feb. 20, 2007</ref>另一巴藉人士亦被盤問，當時他飲醉酒，將其中一個裝有炸彈的手提包拋出車外。<ref name="Reu"/>

